{"tid":2076255,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(求助) 仆街親戚用我老母做諮詢人借咗好多間大耳窿","createTime":"2020-06-23T11:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T13:56:29.000Z","uid":11621,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8d39aaa241f880210a1cfaaca904ae51fbc1fcba","tid":2076255,"uid":11621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:22:18.000Z","msg":"前幾日我老母電話開始收到好多追數訊息<br />\n一睇先知原來個仆街親戚用我老母做諮詢人<br />\n打去問 佢話借落百幾筆電話數 每筆幾千咁 (唔肯定)<br />\n依家佢成家唔知去咗邊撚度匿埋咗 因為佢間屋已經比人淋咗油 同埋就係好似打算走佬<br />\n至於我個邊琴日就收到封手寫紅色大字欠債還錢信 入面有個親戚既身份證副本<br />\n我老母依家已經換咗電話號碼 備咗案 門口亦裝咗cam<br />\n依家我都唔知下一步要點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda8bf944e3c06ff45ca6a5de99e047e94e472c9","tid":2076255,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:22:47.000Z","msg":"賑災基金110萬助廣西水災災民<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2076256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2076256</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a0f8db5cbc7d5a97a52e0c4ee0aa0a8989788e50","tid":2076255,"uid":140802,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:24:06.000Z","msg":"冇簽名都做得依d諮詢人?<br />\n利申唔識"},{"pid":"bdc28e3d5b5c78a1e000349d78b1e2090a330741","tid":2076255,"uid":360551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:25:43.000Z","msg":"諮詢人等於擔保人？"},{"pid":"3481834a5fd5f7923897149c4ebdf495379bf5f7","tid":2076255,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0f8db5cbc7d5a97a52e0c4ee0aa0a8989788e50","tid":2076255,"uid":140802,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:24:06.000Z","msg":"冇簽名都做得依d諮詢人?<br />\n利申唔識"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"我估應該偷影身份證，去財仔求其簽個名就當本人"},{"pid":"a55265ea84b575e1b3fa7e2128507ca7a012ea0f","tid":2076255,"uid":37723,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:27:48.000Z","msg":"講真 親戚不嬲係賊黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無事show off 有事