eplyTime":"2020-06-23T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣，不過我老母同我都被寫做諮詢人<br />\n我上年已經開始<br />\n<br />\n建議唔撚駛理<br />\n搞上你門就報警，當然都係冇用<br />\n但備咗案有咩事班人冇得走<br />\n<br />\n唔係你借真係唔駛驚<br />\n屌返佢老母轉頭都得<br />\n班人都係求財<br />\n你捉鳩你個仆街親戚出嚟迫佢還錢<br />\n或者你爆佢人係邊班大耳窿都唔會搞你"},{"pid":"a09a0e2f3fc7e77d92af36ce671b203a82ed6640","tid":2076255,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:31:56.000Z","msg":"你個親戚仆街黎，要神獸"},{"pid":"71d69d267716396c35944af96a2e2f074dd6ff53","tid":2076255,"uid":323983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a09a0e2f3fc7e77d92af36ce671b203a82ed6640","tid":2076255,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:31:56.000Z","msg":"你個親戚仆街黎，要神獸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"直頭要啦<br />\n我都同樓主差唔多經歷<br />\n老母好撚心軟，陰啲陰啲每個月問我拎錢<br />\n計計埋埋成30幾萬借比個仆街親戚<br />\n上年斷鳩我老母額外家用<br />\n個仆街親戚就借大耳窿寫我地做資詢人<br />\n之後我屌鳩佢做乜撚野寫鳩我地？<br />\n之後佢仆街到話我唔比錢佢佢就問大耳窿借<br />\n嬲撚到我<br />\n屌佢老母真係要私鳥"},{"pid":"0da8c3b1a0971726717666383319e9160a07d284","tid":2076255,"uid":45934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdc28e3d5b5c78a1e000349d78b1e2090a330741","tid":2076255,"uid":360551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:25:43.000Z","msg":"諮詢人等於擔保人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:36:15.000Z","msg":"做擔保人應該要另外簽野，因為個責任大，零保障<br />\n諮詢人似係d 巧立名目嘅野黎<br />\n<br />\n9up"},{"pid":"ac8b504e6397734783b70d08ed5c2513dfd72223","tid":2076255,"uid":45934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:40:48.000Z","msg":"上網求其search <br />\n順利投訴間大耳窿<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cr.gov.hk/tc/services/money-lenders/complaints.htm#utm_source=shop_cr&amp;utm_medium=personal_loans101&amp;utm_campaign=blog&amp;utm_content=loans\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cr.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fservices%2Fmoney-lenders%2Fcomplaints.htm%23utm_source%3Dshop_cr%26utm_medium%3Dpersonal_loans101%26utm_campaign%3Dblog%26utm_content%3Dloans&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JcjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=e3085a01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cr.gov.hk/tc/services/money-lenders/complaints.htm#utm_source=shop_cr&amp;utm_medium=personal_loans101&amp;utm_campaign=blog&amp;utm_content=loans</a>"},{"pid":"ab5eb0784b81b7ea75a9ac31c283fcc56a516b7a","tid":2076255,"uid":260012,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求助 幫人還錢咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n換電話 換地址<br />\n不過你老母應該會比人點左相<br />\n所以一係篤親戚出黎<br />\n一係幫你親戚還<br />\n一係你老母換完地址唔出街 換撚埋電話<br />\n佢就應該追唔到嘅"},{"pid":"a817466999623257fb79be045f09254bbc730040","tid":2076255,"uid":323983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdc28e3d5b5c78a1e000349d78b1e2090a330741","tid":2076255,"uid":360551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:25:43.000Z","msg":"諮詢人等於擔保人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"諮詢人唔駛負責任<br />\n<br />\n擔保人就借錢個條友失蹤就搞你<br />\n<br />\n被做諮詢人一年<br />\n乜事都冇發生過"},{"pid":"85e57bb7b119ac78ad8396dd8365fd7c811b2a73","tid":2076255,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"電話數=正宗大耳窿"},{"pid":"7dc182f21af35e5ab988f82c9433032b26189a9b","tid":2076255,"uid":165886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3481834a5fd5f7923897149c4ebdf495379bf5f7","tid":2076255,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0f8db5cbc7d5a97a52e0c4ee0aa0a8989788e50","tid":2076255,"uid":140802,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:24:06.000Z","msg":"冇簽名都做得依d諮詢人?<br />\n利申唔識"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"我估應該偷影身份證，去財仔求其簽個名就當本人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"係唔洗，住對面屋個仆街就係咁，拎佢啲親戚做擔保，有名有地址就得，可能二三線財仔掛"},{"pid":"ed4dafc19cf21117f9d9c751fde0b0dc148bcc4c","tid":2076255,"uid":140363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0f8db5cbc7d5a97a52e0c4ee0aa0a8989788e50","tid":2076255,"uid":140802,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:24:06.000Z","msg":"冇簽名都做得依d諮詢人?<br />\n利申唔識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T13:42:08.000Z","msg":"佢地會叫你用自己方法叫佢地簽名"},{"pid":"fc47226ae445670564902612a6e771f406914334","tid":2076255,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T13:45:37.000Z","msg":"搞錯呀！咁大整蠱！"},{"pid":"00d9a3e157e7208fd2e9f8c3be2c72f43e54d131","tid":2076255,"uid":178387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T13:51:57.000Z","msg":"理論上諮詢人唔同擔保人，只係好似緊急聯絡人咁，無責任揹條數，如果咩都無簽過又無畀過資料人又唔使太驚，同債主講清楚先"},{"pid":"523c2d99c806366abdcabe12240248695be0d5a3","tid":2076255,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T13:56:29.000Z","msg":"唔洗簽名都會做左<br />\n屋企試過，被淋油，打電話同sms追數<br />\n有個都係變左咨詢人嘅親戚被追上公司<br />\n我屋企就搬左一個月同改電話，之後幾年都間唔中收到信<br />\n<br />\n你係唔係公屋？可以揾區議員幫你攪調遷/ 叫房署出信話冇呢個人<br />\n<br />\n另外都試過呃收數佬，show阿媽張身份證話成家唔同姓<br />\n點知班仆街唔走，我個on9老豆咁岩返黎就認左關自己事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}